@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000

### Upload an art file
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/assets/upload/art
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----CardConjurerBoundary

------CardConjurerBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="nameHint"

sample-art.png
------CardConjurerBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="sample-art.png"
Content-Type: image/png

< ./sample-art.png
------CardConjurerBoundary--

### List art sources for dropdown (local_art + uploaded art)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/assets/art-sources

### List uploaded set symbols
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/assets/sources/set-symbols

### List uploaded watermarks
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/assets/sources/watermarks
